{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I have enough context to outline the work. I\u2019m going to add a typed storage client layer around GCS, centralize path conventions in one strategy module, expose a small smoke-test CLI, update docs and settings where needed, then verify wi...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_21", "text": "I have enough context to outline the work. I\u2019m going to add a typed storage client layer around GCS, centralize path conventions in one strategy module, expose a small smoke-test CLI, update docs and settings where needed, then verify with unit tests plus a live emulator write/read run against the Compose stack.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 45, "prompt_index": 14, "prompt_name": "13 \u2014 Storage Abstraction and Bucket Strategy", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T23:06:58-07:00"}
