{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I\u2019m doing a quick code pass before running the suite. There are a couple of small cleanup points I want to lock down first, mainly around deterministic shutdown and avoiding duplicate bucket-create calls when all logical roles share one...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_50", "text": "I\u2019m doing a quick code pass before running the suite. There are a couple of small cleanup points I want to lock down first, mainly around deterministic shutdown and avoiding duplicate bucket-create calls when all logical roles share one bucket name.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 99, "prompt_index": 14, "prompt_name": "13 \u2014 Storage Abstraction and Bucket Strategy", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T23:16:21-07:00"}
