{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the storage abstraction end to end. The backend now has a typed storage layer in [backend/app/storage](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/storage), a session-scoped path strategy, a GCS-emulator-backed service, app sta...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_93", "text": "Implemented the storage abstraction end to end. The backend now has a typed storage layer in [backend/app/storage](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/storage), a session-scoped path strategy, a GCS-emulator-backed service, app startup wiring in [backend/app/main.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/main.py), a smoke-test CLI plus `make backend-storage-smoke`, and the bucket/prefix doc at [docs/storage-buckets-and-prefixes.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/docs/storage-buckets-and-prefixes.md). I also wrote the required reviewer summary to [prompts/13-storage-abstraction-and-buckets.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/13-storage-abstraction-and-buckets.summary.md).\n\nVerification completed: `make backend-format`, `make backend-format-check`, `make backend-lint`, targeted pytest for storage/health/settings (`14 passed`), full `make backend-test` (`26 passed`), and a live emulator round-trip via `./scripts/dev-compose.sh up -d gcs` plus `make backend-storage-smoke` against `http://127.0.0.1:8568`. I made two checkpoint commits on the current branch: `f1fac4a` and `0d79a61`.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 176, "prompt_index": 14, "prompt_name": "13 \u2014 Storage Abstraction and Bucket Strategy", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T23:21:00-07:00"}
